List of Heroes
==============

Tags: heroes,list

As manager of a heroes agency

* I load the "Dashboard" page
* Then I see the "Top Heroes" header
* I click on the "Heroes" navigation button
* Then I see the "My Heroes" header

Scenario 1: Add a new hero
--------------------------

* I type "Superman" on the "Hero name" field
* I click on the "Add" button
* Then I see "Superman" on the hero's list

Scenario 2: Delete a hero
--------------------------

* I type "Batman" on the "Hero name" field
* I click on the "Add" button
* I delete "Batman" from the hero's list
* Then I don't see "Batman" on the hero's list


